Output demo/recordings/devices.gif
Set Shell bash
Set FontFamily "JetBrainsMono Nerd Font Mono"
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1400
Set Height 800
Set TypingSpeed 80ms
Set Theme "Ayu Mirage"

Hide
Type "./waxon-demo demo"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Show

# Open device picker via command
Type ":device"
Enter
Sleep 1s

# Navigate devices
Type "j"
Sleep 500ms

# Select a device
Enter
Sleep 1.5s

Sleep 1s
